Elastic Search

METADATA (http://www.elastic.co/guide/en/elasticsearch/guide/current/_document_metadata.html)
_index
Where the document lives
 _type
The class of object that the document represents
 _id
The unique identifier for the document

INDEX SAMPLE (http://www.elastic.co/guide/en/elasticsearch/reference/current/docs-index_.html)
$ curl -XPUT 'http://localhost:9200/twitter/tweet/1' -d '{
    "user" : "kimchy",
    "post_date" : "2009-11-15T14:12:12",
    "message" : "trying out Elasticsearch"
}'

{
    "_index" : "twitter",
    "_type" : "tweet",
    "_id" : "1",
    "_version" : 1,
    "created" : true
}

